{"tid":3370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"威斯康星州選委會接獲重新點票要求","createTime":"2016-11-26T06:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T09:38:52.000Z","uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e1411b800b763319c9e2bb75c41f87347c05c7d","tid":3370,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T06:32:54.000Z","msg":"代表美國綠黨參選總統落敗的斯泰因，提出重新點算威斯康星州的選票，當地選委會已接獲要求。當選的特朗普在這個州的得票，較希拉莉多1個百分點、約2萬7千票，全取10張選舉人票。這個州之前8屆大選，都由民主黨候選人勝出。<br />\n<br />\n斯泰因說，有報道稱選民及政黨的電腦被黑客入侵，令人質疑點票系統是否可信。她亦計劃要求密歇根和賓夕法尼亞州重新點票，特朗普在這2個州均贏不足1個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n這3個州合共有46張選舉人票，假如全數推翻結果，理論上足以改變戰局。"},{"pid":"c50c32f19a36f45228aefc7505849f707893997e","tid":3370,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T06:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 左膠又輸打贏要"},{"pid":"84ee88662c51ceb089d679fe86cdfdcff0df9eeb","tid":3370,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T12:32:55.000Z","msg":"Trump haters潛哂水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"974577c1e61297e5e1288a77455fac1c233372a9","tid":3370,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T12:33:56.000Z","msg":"無可能改變結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74427321cfa0c54c03a44ec1af4172350059a42d","tid":3370,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T12:56:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無可能改變結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 但班hilary fans好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b71f60b3af633c7fd737fe59a922c00d90294b3","tid":3370,"uid":22675